    "user_title": "Plan Projects with Research-Based Risk Mitigation",
    "value_statement": "Stop building on assumptions. This skill uses 6-agent research teams and 5-iteration pre-mortem analysis to create evidence-based project plans with less than 3 percent failure confidence.",
    "seo_keywords": [
      "Claude Code planning",
      "research-driven development",
      "multi-agent consensus",
